sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Controller as OrderV1Controller
    participant Facade as OrderFacade
    participant ProductService
    participant OrderService
    participant DB

    User->>Controller: POST /api/v1/orders (items)
    Note over Controller: Interceptor에서 loginId/loginPw 검증 후 userId 주입
    Controller->>Facade: createOrder(userId, items)

    Facade->>ProductService: validateAndGetProducts(items)
    ProductService->>DB: SELECT products + product_stocks WHERE id IN (...)

    alt 존재하지 않는 상품 포함
        ProductService-->>Facade: CoreException(NOT_FOUND)
        Facade-->>Controller: CoreException
        Controller-->>User: 404 Not Found
    else 재고 부족
        ProductService-->>Facade: CoreException(BAD_REQUEST)
        Facade-->>Controller: CoreException
        Controller-->>User: 400 Bad Request
    else 정상
        ProductService-->>Facade: List~ProductModel~ (스냅샷용)
    end

    Facade->>OrderService: createOrder(userId, snapshotItems)
    OrderService->>DB: INSERT orders (status = ORDERED)
    OrderService->>DB: INSERT order_items (productName, unitPrice 스냅샷)
    OrderService-->>Facade: OrderModel

    loop 각 item
        Facade->>ProductService: decreaseStock(productId, quantity)
        ProductService->>DB: UPDATE product_stocks SET quantity = quantity - ?
    end

    Facade-->>Controller: OrderInfo
    Controller-->>User: 201 Created ApiResponse(OrderResponse)
